oduced by the customers that buy its products.\", \"from\": 741, \"to\": 928, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Scope\", \"from\": 772, \"to\": 777}, {\"ngram\": \"3 targets\", \"from\": 778, \"to\": 787}, {\"ngram\": \"any business\", \"from\": 825, \"to\": 837}, {\"ngram\": \"the carbon\", \"from\": 869, \"to\": 879}, {\"ngram\": \"the customers\", \"from\": 892, \"to\": 905}, {\"ngram\": \"its products\", \"from\": 915, \"to\": 927}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Shell heavily promoted its net zero target in Australia, while internal emails shown to a US government committee revealed it was 'not a Shell business plan'.\", \"from\": 930, \"to\": 1089, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 931, \"end\": 936, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shell_plc\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 7.860622116857729e-12, \"text\": \"Shell\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shell_plc\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shell_plc\"}, {\"begin\": 977, \"end\": 986, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9988615834517636, \"rank\": 0.001139714005527662, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 1021, \"end\": 1023, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_government_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999197469277736, \"rank\": 4.614946404822202e-05, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_government_of_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_government_of_the_United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1068, \"end\": 1073, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shell_plc\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 7.860622116857729e-12, \"text\": \"Shell\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shell_plc\", \"dbp