ling down on oil and gas and damaging their own credibility in the process.\\\"\", \"from\": 1829, \"to\": 2080, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Agencies\", \"from\": 1830, \"to\": 1838}, {\"ngram\": \"the account\", \"from\": 1880, \"to\": 1891}, {\"ngram\": \"the renewables transition\", \"from\": 1914, \"to\": 1939}, {\"ngram\": \"the brand\", \"from\": 1975, \"to\": 1984}, {\"ngram\": \"corporation\", \"from\": 1988, \"to\": 1999}, {\"ngram\": \"oil\", \"from\": 2017, \"to\": 2020}, {\"ngram\": \"gas\", \"from\": 2025, \"to\": 2028}, {\"ngram\": \"their own credibility\", \"from\": 2042, \"to\": 2063}, {\"ngram\": \"the process\", \"from\": 2067, \"to\": 2078}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Brisbane-based agency Nous had worked with Shell Energy to deliver its campaigns, including the brand's net zero work, in 2022.\", \"from\": 2082, \"to\": 2209, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2104, \"end\": 2108, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nous\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nous\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nous\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nous\"}, {\"begin\": 2125, \"end\": 2137, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shell_Energy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shell Energy\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shell_Energy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shell_Energy\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Brisbane-based agency\", \"from\": 2082, \"to\": 2103}, {\"ngram\": \"its campaigns\", \"from\": 2149, \"to\": 2162}, {\"ngram\": \"the brand's net zero work\", \"from\": 2174, \"to\": 2199}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There has been growing scrutiny of agencies and their work with fossil fuel companies.\", \"from\": 2211, \"to\": 2297, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"There has been growing scrutiny\", \"from\": 2211, \"to\": 2242}, {\"ngram\": \"agencies\", \"from\": 2246, \"to\": 2254}, {\"n