e/Benefit_corporation\"}, {\"begin\": 2517, \"end\": 2522, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Havas\", \"score\": 0.8117654572850512, \"rank\": 0.23188291768973535, \"text\": \"Havas\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Havas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Havas\"}, {\"begin\": 2541, \"end\": 2546, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shell_plc\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 7.860622116857729e-12, \"text\": \"Shell\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shell_plc\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shell_plc\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"26 communications\", \"from\": 2426, \"to\": 2443}, {\"ngram\": \"advertising agencies\", \"from\": 2448, \"to\": 2468}, {\"ngram\": \"an official complaint\", \"from\": 2479, \"to\": 2500}, {\"ngram\": \"involvement\", \"from\": 2524, \"to\": 2535}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Havas' decision to make its B Corps a part of Shell's misleading marketing is a clear threat to the integrity and brand of the B Corp movement.\", \"from\": 2549, \"to\": 2693, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2550, \"end\": 2555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Havas\", \"score\": 0.8117654572850512, \"rank\": 0.23188291768973535, \"text\": \"Havas\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Havas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Havas\"}, {\"begin\": 2578, \"end\": 2585, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/II_Army_Corps_(Greece)\", \"score\": 0.9999999760434551, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"B Corps\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/II_Army_Corps_(Greece)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/II_Army_Corps_(Greece)\"}, {\"begin\": 2596, \"end\": 2601, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shell_plc\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 7.860622116857729e-12, \"text\": \"Shell\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shell_plc\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shell_plc\"}, {\"begin\": 2677, \"end\": 2683, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benefit_corporation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6660233435840136e-28, \"text\": \"B Corp\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benefit_corporation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benefit_corporation\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a clear threat\", \"from\": 2628, \"to\": 2642}, {\"ngram\": \"the integrity\", \"from\": 2646, \"to\": 2659}, {\"ngram\": \"brand\", \"from\": 2664, \"to\": 2669}]}, {\"sentence\": \"B Corps should not be producing marketing and PR for the world's biggest polluters, and we are grateful to B Lab for continuing this investigation so that their many members who support serious climate action can be heard,\\\" said Clean Creatives executive director Duncan Meisel at the time.\", \"from\": 2694, \"to\": 2984, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2694, \"end\": 2701, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/II_Army_Corps_(Greece)\", \"score\": 0.9999999760434551, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"B Corps\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/II_Army_Corps_(Greece)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/II_Army_Corps_(Greece)\"}, {\"begin\": 2958, \"end\": 2964, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/King_Duncan\", \"score\": 0.9999985852333342, \"rank\": 1.3801132454518519e-06, \"text\": \"Duncan\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/King_Duncan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/King_Duncan\"}, {\"begin\": 2965, \"end\": 2971, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steven_Meisel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Meisel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steven_Meisel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steven_Meisel\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"marketing\", \"from\": 2726, \"to\": 2735}, {\"ngram\": \"PR\", \"from\": 2740, \"to\": 2742}, {\"ngram\": \"the world's biggest polluters\", \"from\": 2747, \"to\": 2776}, {\"ngram\": \"B Lab\", \"from\": 2801, \"to\": 2806}, {\"ngram\": \"this investigation\", \"from\": 2822, \"to\": 2840}, {\"ngram\": \"their many members\", \"from\": 2849, \"to\": 2867}, {\"ngram\": \"serious climate action\", \"from\": 2880, \"to\": 2902}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 2975, \"to\": 2983}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Noble added that the EU is about to usher in new greenwashing rules that will prohibit the use of vague environmental claims such as \\\"environmentally friendly,\\\" \\\"natural,\\\" \\\"biodegradable,\\\" \\\"climate neutral,\\\" or \\\"eco\\\" unless these claims can be backed up by adequate evidence.\", \"from\": 2986, \"to\": 3261, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3007, \"end\": 3009, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Union\", \"score\": 0.9999999999922693, \"rank\": 7.877943922214742e-12, \"text\": \"EU\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Union\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Union\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Noble\", \"from\": 2986, \"to\": 2991}, {\"ngram\": \"new greenwashing rules\", \"from\": 3031, \"to\": 3053}, {\"ngram\": \"the use\", \"from\": 3073, \"to\": 3080}, {\"ngram\": \"vague environmental claims\", \"from\": 3084, \"to\": 3110}, {\"ngram\": \"these claims\", \"from\": 3210, \"to\": 3222}, {\"ngram\": \"adequate evidence\", \"from\": 3243, \"to\": 3260}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"These laws are expected to transform the sustainability advertising landscape, both in the EU and outside, as companies will be selling into the EU, the world's largest trading bloc,\\\" said Noble.\", \"from\": 3263, \"to\": 3459, \"entities\": [{\"begin\"